(2654, 'Physiotherapy for Critical Care Nursing', 'PHY213.04 Objectives', 'Percussion and shaking are used clinically for one of the following reason,', '["To dislodge secretion", "To increase vital capacity", "Increase tidal volume", "Promote accumulation of secretion"]'::jsonb, 3, '', 'Rehabilitation & Mobilization', '🏃', true),
