(2698, 'Post-Operative Complications', 'ICU Self Assessment Practice Session', 'Nerve damage is a potential postoperative complication in the ICU. What assessment finding should the nurse be alert for?', '["Muscle weakness", "Increased heart rate", "Elevated temperature", "Decreased respiratory rate"]'::jsonb, 0, '', 'Mixed Revision', '📚', true),
