(2701, 'Post-Operative Complications', 'ICU Self Assessment Practice Session', 'Nutritional deficiencies can occur postoperatively in the ICU. Which vitamin deficiency is commonly seen insurgical patients?', '["Vitamin A", "Vitamin B12", "Vitamin C", "Vitamin D"]'::jsonb, 1, '', 'Mixed Revision', '📚', true),
